-- 20_multifile.pak
-- Demonstrates: module declaration and cross-file structure.
-- Status: [PARTIAL]
--
-- In a multi-file project, declare the module path at the top of each file.
-- The entry block lives in only one file (typically main.pak).
-- Other files declare their module path and are imported via 'use'.

module main

-- use other.module   -- would import another file's module

entry {
    -- entry block exists in only one file per project
}
